    "meta_description": "The Kids curriculum at Quantum is based on Tae Kwon Do, a martial art from Korea. Tae Kwon Do translated from Korean means “hand/foot/art.” In many TKD schools, tournaments are the main focus for the students to measure their progress and achievement. This is not the case at Quantum: we provide a place for young people to learn…",
